FBIS4-45584 "jptdd028__l94084" JPRS-TDD-94-028-L JPRS Narcotics 20 June 1994 EAST EUROPE BULGARIA Smuggler of 6.6 Kg of Heroin Receives Six Year Sentence Smuggler of 6.6 Kg of Heroin Receives Six Year Sentence AU2106100494 Sofia BTA in English 1447 GMT 20 Jun 94 AU2106100494 Sofia BTA English BFN ["Today"--BTA lead] [Excerpt] Sofia, June 20 (BTA) -- [passage omitted] The Ruse (on the Danube) regional court sentenced a Dutch citizen of Turkish descent to six years in prison and a fine of 200,000 leva for attempting to smuggle across the border 6.6 kg of heroin. The case was heard behind closed doors, said BTA's local correspondent. [passage omitted]
